# Problem 1.f )
x = dist
y = CollegeDistance$ed
Sxy = sum((x - mean(x))*(y - mean(y)))
Sxx = sum((x - mean(x))^2)
Syy = sum((y - mean(y))^2)
#c(Sxy, Sxx, Syy)

SSR=(Sxx*Syy-Sxy^2)/Sxx
#SSR
